    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>remaining Brussels sprouts</strong> finely</p><p>Once the onion and sprouts have softened slightly, drain your<strong> king prawns</strong>, then add to the pan and cook for an initial 1-2 min</p>",
