    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of <strong>cooked white long grain rice </strong>to separate the grains</p><p>After an initial 1-2 min, add the <strong>sliced Brussels sprouts</strong> and <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until the rice is hot and the prawns are cooked through</p>",
