    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>to the pan with the <strong>remaining toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>king prawn & sprout fried rice</strong></p>",
